libsoup: libsoup (HTTP library)
libsoup:
libsoup: libsoup is an HTTP client/server library for GNOME. It uses GObjects 
libsoup: and the glib main loop, to integrate well with GNOME applications. It 
libsoup: features both asynchronous and synchronous APIs, SSL Support using GnuTLS, 
libsoup: proxy support, including authentication and SSL tunneling, client support 
libsoup: for Digest, NTLM, and Basic authentication, server support for Digest and 
libsoup: Basic authentication, and basic client-side SOAP and XML-RPC support.
